651.raw: #Anon, upon losing his job, heads home, only to end up in an abandoned facility. But hey, at least they have Wi-Fi. The tale of a man who awakens in a mysterious lab... and quickly realizes he's not alone. Inspired by a dream, begun on a whim, and intended to end in a single weekend, Terminal Condition quickly ballooned into a full-length feature. It's also my personal favorite finished work, featuring one of my absolute favorite "Retverse" characters. See if you can guess who it is.
